snippet.title: JUMP FORCE – Shoto Todoroki Trailer
snippet.description:
The battle is heating up with Todoroki's arrival to #JumpForce! Power up your quirk to freeze your opponent and help return order to our world!

More characters are on their way to JUMP FORCE, who would you like to see next? bandainam.co/JumpForcePO
